cu.explanation_en: Changing the NG-AMF interface IP address to a different subnet (192.168.9.43) creates an unreachable IP range conflict, preventing CU from establishing proper NG-AMF connections and causing interface failures.

du.explanation_en: Altering the PRACH message 1 frequency start by one unit introduces frequency misalignment, leading to RACH procedure failures and potential cell access issues in the DU.
